column5: How's fishing today?  We are thinking about heading out tomorrow and not sure if we should just cancel to end the season, the cold front came few days ago, and not sure if it would have shut down bass fishing condition.  Shore Salmon fishing was not good last two days. It was freezing cold at night, with strong wind chill factor.  It will get a little bit warmer again tomorrow.
bass fishing was good for me today and it was freeeeeezing
I was fishing Friday morning and it was freezing, but I did well. Seven decent bass in a couple hours. I think the fall bite is on!
I'd rather fish a cold front, than pack it in for the year.....I say screw it and go!!  P.S....why are you putting the boat away so early?  Sinker
